{"tid":1312510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡易DIY 防禦，work唔work?","createTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:54:16.000Z","uid":262301,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0366359eda0adc9bc5a1fac5d5dab3d9caa301","tid":1312510,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"Source 九龍冰室 - 九紋龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OV7yXxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOV7yXxV.png&h=014ef9a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如防警棍<br />\n遇襲時本能地會用手去擋，可以護到上半身<br />\n（水喉通可能效果更好）<br />\n<br />\n易於隱藏但長袖會熱撚死<br />\n<br />\n唔好唸會唔會被狗屈你收藏攻擊性武器，反正佢要屈嘅話，你帶條鎖匙係身佢都一樣老屈<br />\n<br />\n有無法律撚可以解答下，咁樣DIY出街、被搜，有無犯法？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依類都收到係衫袖，好似唔係咁易入手，而且手柄外露難以收藏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBd2QVF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBd2QVF.png&h=1dcd5484&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請大家唔好見到p牌就負皮，討論下"},{"pid":"9abe4c41cf7b64f341880628cbe450d08979d03a","tid":1312510,"uid":264965,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"Brad Pitt 話用雜誌圍實前臂OK<br />\n<img src=\"https://moderncombatandsurvival.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wwz_body_armor_blog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoderncombatandsurvival.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F08%2Fwwz_body_armor_blog.jpg&h=ade25df4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc2855cafd4ae27ca194ebb70069ef92284a2540","tid":1312510,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9abe4c41cf7b64f341880628cbe450d08979d03a","tid":1312510,"uid":264965,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"Brad Pitt 話用雜誌圍實前臂OK<br />\n<img src=\"https://moderncombatandsurvival.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/wwz_body_armor_blog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoderncombatandsurvival.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F0